data = pd.read_csv('california_housing_train.csv')
data
columnsData = data.columns;
X=data[data.columns[:-1]]
y=data[data.columns[-1]]*1
target_names=data.columns[-1]
feature_names=data.columns[:-1]
number_of_features = X.shape[1]
number_of_classes = len(np.unique(y))
print("Number and names of classes:", len(np.unique(y)), target_names) #The number of classes is the number of unique values of the y vector
print("Number and names of features:", X.shape[1], feature_names) #The number of features is equal to the amount of columns in the X matrix
print("Number of data points:", X.shape[0]) #The number of datapoints is equal to the amount of rows in the X matrix

In [64]:
alphas = [0.1, 1, 10, 100, 1e3, 1e4, 2e4, 5e4, 8e4, 1e5, 1e6, 1e7, 1e8]
reg = RidgeCV(alphas=alphas, store_cv_values=True)
reg.fit(X_train, y_train)
print("Best alpha using built-in RidgeCV: %f" % reg.alpha_)
print("Coefficients W")
print(reg.coef_)
print("Intercept W0")
print(reg.intercept_ )
y_pred = reg.predict(X_test)
print("Error")
print(mean_squared_error(y_test, y_pred))
plt.figure()
plt.plot(np.arange(len(reg.coef_)), reg.coef_, ".",  markersize=15, color = "darkgreen")
plt.xlabel("Feature number")
plt.ylabel("Coefficients w")
plt.title("Coefficient Weights")
plt.show()

In [60]:
from sklearn.pipeline import make_pipeline
reg = make_pipeline(PolynomialFeatures(2), LinearRegression())
reg.fit(X_train, y_train)

y_pred = reg.predict(X_test)
print("Error")
print(mean_squared_error(y_test, y_pred))
print("Coefficient Mean", np.mean(reg.named_steps['linearregression'].coef_))
print("Coefficient Max", np.max(reg.named_steps['linearregression'].coef_))
print("Coefficient Min", np.min(reg.named_steps['linearregression'].coef_))
print("Total number of coefficients", len(reg.named_steps['linearregression'].coef_))
print("Zero weight coefficients", len(reg.named_steps['linearregression'].coef_[reg.named_steps['linearregression'].coef_==0]))


plt.figure()
plt.plot(np.arange(len(reg.named_steps['linearregression'].coef_)), reg.named_steps['linearregression'].coef_, ".",  markersize=15, color = "darkgreen")
plt.xlabel("Feature number")
plt.ylabel("Coefficients w")
plt.title("Coefficient Weights")
plt.show()
